{"tid":2250570,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 嘉寶漢堡","createTime":"2020-10-20T07:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T13:04:31.000Z","uid":310853,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e1163da23fb8e938cbde506799884a0b8ba3697d","tid":2250570,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T07:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9jUwtP3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9jUwtP3.png&h=ec7ce12c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽咗好耐 今日去試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nX9ZXH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nX9ZXH.png&h=9ad8d45b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗌咗個黑松露牛堡同蝦堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n薯條我就自己覺得麻麻地<br />\n因為我鍾意食幼身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icD1Q5A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicD1Q5A.png&h=b457c8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個黑松露牛堡係好好食<br />\n勁重黑松露味 估唔到咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vShJ4rO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvShJ4rO.png&h=db875d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個蝦堡就唔係我嘅 咬咗兩啖<br />\n兩啖都有蝦肉 真係真材實料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整體嚟講係相當唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6837dea775efb4c3f9d3fec38ad23ec444d00885","tid":2250570,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"又食生日飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9089f686575497c3406013535c3583eccd846e2","tid":225057